                    </a>
                    {{/if}}
                </span>
            </nav>
        </header>
        <h1>Too Long; Didn't Read</h1>
        <div class="content">
            A link aggregation site. Kind of like a terrible version of another site whose name rhymes with "Fed it.".

            {{{ body }}}
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
